            "prompt": {
                "question": "<p>What is the key factor that organizations need to address for the success of Data Governance (DG)?</p>",
                "relatedLectureIds": [],
                "links": [],
                "feedbacks": [
                    "Implementing data management projects is important for overall data management success, but it is not the key factor specifically for the success of Data Governance (DG). Data Governance focuses on establishing policies, processes, and controls to ensure data is managed effectively and meets organizational needs.",
